title: U2 - US Festival 5-30-1983 - VIDEO OF ENTIRE SHOW RARE!

This is a FLV file so if your having problems playing use windows media player classic or vlc.
Also this is not the best quality will be looking into a upgrade of this soon which will be far superior!


U2
5-30-1983
US Festival
Glen Helen Park
Devore, CA
55 minutes
Pro Shot



This is U 2's performance at the U.S. Festival in May of 1983.   See the Edge with hair and Bono with his mullet as the Irish band performs their hearts out.   Bono even climbs the stage scaffolding at one point.   This performance wasn't just days before the famous Red Rocks show in Denver.  A must have for U2 fans.  Tracks are as follows:
